column5: Hi. trying to bye # 10 and #13 Colorado blades, cant find them anywhere. Any one know?
dont even think they make them that big, the biggest I have seen and on most musky baits are a size 8, meaning eight inches long in colorado  #10 and #13  would be huge!!
try hagens. they have whats needed
Just recieved a large order of bait parts last week. www.staminainc.com  They deff. have what your looking for.
Thank you for your input. Stamina has the BIG blades  Just no #13 . Thanks again
